  "text": "A digital pathology image resource. We used the molecular pathology arm of the large breast study SEARCH for this work [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . This is a population based study of women from the east of England with breast cancer. We included 2258 breast tumours and have made digital images for all three markers and reported algorithms freely accessible at: https://www. cri.cam.ac.uk/data/cclab/; username: cclabpub; password: uwzuhq8n.",
